race.comment: DAINTREE DAZZLER (7) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (19.59) behind ALL IN OLLIE at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can find winning form. REDGUM WARS (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.63) at this track behind Bullseye Bob in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Leading player again. BUFFALO COWBOY (5) was below best last time when fourth but three back was a Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. DONEGAL EXPRESS (1) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.
